        <updateDate>2006-11-22T21:16:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Servicemembers' Cellular Phone Contract Fairness Act of 2006 - Amends the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act to allow members of the Armed Forces who are called to active duty for a period of not less than 90 days to cancel or suspend their cell phone contracts without incurring early termination or reactivation fees.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
